duties_responsibilities.duty: Operate warehouse equipment including Reach Truck, Motorized Double Pallet Jack, and Dock Stocker (counter-balance)
Receive items into SAP and accurately put items into correct warehouse locations
Verify received items match the item ordered and perform pallet wrapping and product de-casing
Unpack, sort, and count parts from vendors' purchase orders
Notify receiving issues of all discrepancies in a timely manner and perform general maintenance and cleaning
